HEADWORD: Strapping
<hw>Strap"ping</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Tall; strong;
lusty; large; <as>as, a <ex>strapping</ex> fellow</as>.</def>
<mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>There are five and thirty <qex>strapping</qex> officers gone.</q>
<rj><qau>Farquhar.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Strapple</ent>⟦br⟧
